name: Manetsip
body:
### Welcome to the home of the P2P-SIP over MANET project at Carleton University!
We will investigate how to come up with secure and effective deployments of SIP VOIP in a hierarchical MANET setting. More detail forthcoming!

### The team:
Babak Esfandiari (@esfandia), Professor.
Thomas Kunz (@thomashanskunz), Professor.
Francois Gagnon, Adjunct Professor.
Alan Davoust, Postdoc.
Mahmoud Raslan, Postdoc.
Alexandre Cormier (@alexcormier), Master's student.
Silas Echegini, Master's student.
Frank Ockenfeld, visiting student.

### The papers:
Coming soon, we hope!
